parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt pretensioner can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the airbag warning light to illuminate and the airbags to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
a beeping or chiming noise is heard
the airbag system malfunctions
and the airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
a beeping or chiming noise is heard
and the airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to suddenly accelerate, which can increase the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates
the rear brakes lock
and the airbags fail to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without warning
even when the brake pedal is depressed; the engine RPMs increase rapidly; the vehicle surges forward; the accelerator pedal is difficult to depress.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the throttle body assembly can cause unintended acceleration, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine RPMs increase rapidly; the vehicle surges forward; the accelerator pedal is difficult to depress; the throttle body assembly needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunction of the cruise control system can cause unintended acceleration, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates abnormally when utilizing cruise control; the vehicle does not respond to deactivation of cruise control; the engine RPMs increase rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The steering becomes tight or hard
the steering wheel is difficult to maneuver
the power steering assist fails without warning
excessive force is needed to steer the vehicle
the steering wheel does not respond to input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the steering shaft can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering shaft is fractured and detaching
the power steering pulley and shaft are fractured
the engine is overheating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering rack needs to be replaced
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel does not respond to input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel does not lock when the engine is turned off
the steering column and gear went out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly repair vehicles under recall can lead to continued safety issues and potential accidents.
symptoms: The recall repair was not completed
the parts needed for the recall repair were not available
the vehicle was not approved for the recall repair due to other damages.
